headline: Lockheed Martin downgraded as cash flow concerns cloud defense outlook
summary: Investing.com -- JPMorgan downgraded Lockheed Martin to Neutral, saying its longer-term cash flow outlook looks weaker than the market expects, even as demand across aerospace and defense remains broadly strong into 2026.
